    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/fr-hellodarknessmyoldfriend/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=609001508167484338&sectionId=609001508268213170)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ0_wHcqSP_text","label":"ggQ0_wHcqSP_text","default":"<strong>FAQs</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_0","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_0","default":"<p>How soon will I see results?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_1","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_1","default":"<p>Will this cause bloating like other collagen powders?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_2","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_2","default":"<p>What does Glowactiv™ taste like?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_3","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_3","default":"<p>How do I take Glowactiv?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_4","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_4","default":"<p>What’s the difference between Glowactiv and other collagens?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_5","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_5","default":"<p>Can I take your products whilst pregnant or breastfeeding?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_6","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_6","default":"<p>Why should I start with the 60 Day 4-Tub Bundle?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_7","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_7","default":"<p>What if I don't see results?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_8","label":"ggqGhy0jyiD_childItem_8","default":"<p>What does reaching my \"Glow Peak\" actually mean?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGssONvXbo_text","label":"ggGssONvXbo_text","default":"<p>90% of users report visible results <strong>within 60 days</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Days 1–14: The Reset</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>Experience improved digestive comfort and reduced bloating as the <strong>Tri-Phase Support System™</strong> clears the \"Bloat Block\" and prepares your system for absorption.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Days 15–45: The Build</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>Hydration levels rise and skin texture begins to smooth as bioactive marine peptides support the structural foundation of your skin, hair, and nails.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 60: The Glow Peak</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>Enjoy a visible \"bounce\" in skin elasticity and significant new hair density as you reach your <strong>Glow Peak</strong>—the result of 60 days of uninterrupted cellular renewal.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_NGecSUd0_text","label":"gg_NGecSUd0_text","default":"<p>No. Unlike generic \"Naked Peptides\" that often cause digestive upset, Glowactiv™ is engineered for comfort. Our formula includes prebiotics and probiotics to ensure a 0% bloat, 100% comfort experience that is gentle on your digestive tract.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR-TgPk4IM_text","label":"ggR-TgPk4IM_text","default":"<p>We offer three profiles designed to blend seamlessly into your daily ritual:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Superfruit:</strong> A vibrant, naturally sweet fruit infusion for a refreshing water ritual.</p><p><strong>Blueberry</strong>: A refreshing, real-fruit burst perfect for water and smoothies.</p><p><strong>Iced Coffee</strong>: A creamy, smooth morning energy boost.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>All flavors use enzymatically processed Marine Peptides to ensure zero \"fishy\" aftertaste or chalky texture.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggc44bVgN4-_text","label":"ggc44bVgN4-_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#2D2926;font-size:px;\">However you like, just make sure you're having it daily to reach your Glow Peak! We recommend adding to water: use your high-speed whisk, shake in your bottle, or stir with a spoon. Alternatively, blend it into a smoothie, add to fresh juice, or mix it into your morning oats.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6jjT-tzwE_text","label":"gg6jjT-tzwE_text","default":"<p>Standard \"Naked Peptides\" (usually bovine) often fall into the \"Bio-Availability Gap,\" meaning they are harder for your body to absorb and often cause bloating. Glowactiv™ is built on our 3-in-1 Glow Matrix™, which uses premium Marine Collagen—proven to be up to 1.5x more bio-available than bovine alternatives.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>While others just provide protein, our Tri-Phase Glow Support System™ prepares your gut for absorption, supplies the peptides, and then locks in results with Vitamin C and 25 superfood co-factors. It’s the difference between a single ingredient and a complete biological infrastructure for your skin, hair, and nails.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0PugZb8hr_text","label":"gg0PugZb8hr_text","default":"<p>Our products contain only clean and natural ingredients that are regularly tested for contaminants or chemicals. While our ingredients are of the highest quality, we are not medically qualified to advise on suitability during pregnancy or breastfeeding. We always recommend consulting with a medical professional before starting any new supplement. All ingredients are clearly listed on our website for your review.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaLQpIq_nF_text","label":"ggaLQpIq_nF_text","default":"<p>Real structural change in your skin, hair, and nails follows your body's natural 60-day cellular renewal cycle—it doesn't happen overnight.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- <strong>The 60-Day Window</strong>: Weeks 1–4 focus on the \"Reset\" (gut comfort and hydration), while the most visible results happen between weeks 5–8 as you reach your Glow Peak.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- <strong>Uninterrupted Consistency</strong>: This bundle ensures you have a 60-day supply, which is the \"only secret\" to deep cellular results.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- <strong>Unbeatable Value</strong>: Reach your peak for just $1.98/day. You’ll save $69 and unlock $71 in free ritual gifts (Pro-Frother, Hydrator Bottle, and Digital Guides).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- <strong>Glow Peak Guarantee</strong>: We are so confident in this 60-day protocol that if you don't see noticeable results after 4 tubs, we’ll refund you in full.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggx4WepX4ed_text","label":"ggx4WepX4ed_text","default":"<p>We’ve removed the risk so you can focus on the ritual. Our 60-Day 'Glow Peak' Guarantee is designed to give your body the full time needed for a structural renewal.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you follow the protocol for 60 days and don’t see a visible transformation in skin density, hair strength, or nail health, we will refund your entire purchase. Your journey to your Glow Peak should be as effortless as our daily scoop.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDFbLvIiDu_text","label":"ggDFbLvIiDu_text","default":"<p>The \"Glow Peak\" is the point where the cumulative effects of the <strong>3-in-1 Glow Matrix™</strong> become fully visible. Because our formula works from the inside out, results happen in distinct stages. For most, this begins with a noticeable improvement in gut comfort within the first 14 days, followed by a visible transformation in skin hydration and hair vitality as the <strong>Tri-Phase Glow Support System™</strong> completes its full cycle by day 60.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The 60-Day Glow Transformation Timeline</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Days 1–14: The Prep Phase</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>• Our system begins by preparing your gut for optimal comfort.</p><p>• During this phase, you may notice reduced bloating and more consistent daily energy as the 25+ superfoods and gut support co-factors begin to take effect.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Days 15–45: The Supply Phase</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>• This is the stage where your body consistently receives high-quality marine collagen peptides.</p><p>• You will likely notice \"softer\" skin and improved hydration levels as the <strong>3-in-1 Glow Matrix™</strong> begins replacing your old, cluttered supplement shelf.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Days 45–60: The Support Phase (The Glow Peak)</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>• During the final phase, we support your progress with Vitamin C and superfood co-factors to maximize collagen synthesis.</p><p>• This is when most customers reach their <strong>Glow Peak</strong>, leading to noticeably stronger nails, reduced hair shedding, and a more radiant skin tone.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNwcLuA8TC_label","label":"ggNwcLuA8TC_label","default":"<p>BUY NOW | UP TO 37% OFF</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf1SoDSyYz_text","label":"ggf1SoDSyYz_text","default":"<p><strong>LIMITED TIME • FREE BOTTLE, FROTHER &amp; RECIPE BOOK</strong></p>"}],
